## Environment Variables Per Deploy Context

```
Netlify Dashboard → Site configuration → Environment variables

For each variable, set scope:
  Production        → only runs on main/master branch deploys
  Deploy Previews   → PR preview deploys
  Branch Deploys    → all non-main branches
  All               → everywhere

Supabase keys per context:
  Production: NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL = https://[prod-ref].supabase.co
  Deploy Previews: NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL = https://[staging-ref].supabase.co
  (when using Supabase Branching integration, these are injected automatically)
```

