## Deploy Hooks — Trigger Redeployment

```bash
# Create deploy hook: Netlify → Site → Build hooks → Add
# Use case: trigger rebuild when content changes in Supabase

# Example: pg_cron job that triggers a Netlify rebuild at 3am (for ISR content refresh)
SELECT cron.schedule('nightly-rebuild', '0 3 * * *', $$
  SELECT net.http_post(
    url := 'https://api.netlify.com/build_hooks/YOUR_HOOK_ID',
    body := '{}'::JSONB
  )
$$);
```

