## Common Netlify + Next.js Issues

| Error | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `Error: ENOENT .next/routes-manifest.json` | Forgot `publish = ".next"` in netlify.toml | Add `[build] publish = ".next"` |
| 404 on dynamic routes after deploy | Missing `_redirects` or wrong publish dir | Ensure `publish = ".next"` not `out` |
| API routes timeout | Default 10s Netlify function timeout | Dashboard → Functions → Timeout → increase to 26s |
| Env vars undefined in build | Wrong scope set in Netlify dashboard | Set env var scope to "All" or correct context |
| `cookies()` error in middleware | Not using `@supabase/ssr` correctly | Use `createServerClient` not `createClient` in middleware |
| Images not loading from Supabase | Missing `remotePatterns` | Add Supabase hostname to `next.config.ts` |

