## Netlify Functions Limits vs Supabase Edge Functions

```
Netlify Functions (serverless):
  Max timeout: 10s (can increase to 26s on paid)
  Request body: 6MB
  Memory: 3008MB
  Concurrency: unlimited (but cold starts)

Netlify Background Functions:
  Max timeout: 15 minutes
  No response returned (fire-and-forget)

Netlify Edge Functions:
  Max timeout: 30s
  Memory: 128MB

Supabase Edge Functions:
  Max timeout: 150s request (400s background)
  CPU: 2s
  Memory: 150MB
  Bundle: 20MB

Use Netlify Background Functions for: PDF generation, report emails, bulk imports
Use Supabase Edge Functions for: DB operations, AI calls, webhooks with Supabase auth
```
